<plot>A monstrous comedy with heart, SHOWDOWN OF THE GODZ demonstrates what devotion to Japanese monster movies can do to a marriage and career. SHOWDOWN OF THE GODZ tells the story of Jesse, the world's biggest Japanese monster movie fan, who is challenged to a Japanese monster movie trivia showdown with the soon-to-retire 84-year-old archivist from Toho Studios. Can Jesse keep his marriage and job intact as he trains for the big event?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?494828</url></doc>
